:: Ship1
<<set $speed to 3>>
<<set $defense to 6>>
<<set $attack to 10>>
You look across the port and spot a ship that has been made for combat. 
The hull is a midnight shade of black with crimson red sails. 
The crew is filled with a varity of members who seem to have not so open arms at first glance. 
It seems you will need to gain their respect and prove your addition towards their cause. 
This ship's title is 'The Plague'
[[You see the captain of the black ship.|Black Captain]]
