:: Ship3
<<set $speed to 10>>
<<set $defense to 3>>
<<set $attack to 5>>
On the far side of the port you manage to locate a rather small ship. 
This ship's hull is a faded green with bleach white sails. 
The ship itself and the crew it holds is not much to look at however, you can tell it can get you anywhere you would want to go in a matter of moments. 
This ship's title is unknown....
