:: Black Captain
This ship's Captain is known as Scur-V the most feared pirate to ever live. 
It is said that he once single handedly took out an entire armada with only a single canon. 
His apperance is as unwelcoming as his crew. 
He has a long white beard and what should be a foot a peg takes its place.
