:: Brown Captain
This ship's captain is known to be the most respectable man across the seven seas. 
He calls himself The Collector. He is as well dressed as his crewmates and is hold what seems to be a very expensive wine glass and bottle. 
He carries a joyful smile as he mingles with the people around, clearly proud at what he has accomplished.
